name: Oversteper
description:
Sometimes, in order to take a step away, closer to or through something, you need a guide. I had such a guide, although none of us then realised the episodic nature of our roles in each other's lives. But is it possible to know about this beforehand?

Not particularly interested in my plans, she walked me a short way through what I could have overcome for years, and then gently, but not without bitterness, pushed me out onto the road.
